# BizFlow - Environment Variables Template

## Backend Configuration (.env)

### Database
DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://user:password@localhost:5432/bizflow
MYSQL_URL=mysql+aiomysql://user:password@localhost:3306/bizflow

### Redis
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379

### JWT Authentication
SECRET_KEY=your-super-secret-key-change-in-production
ALGORITHM=HS256
ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES=30
REFRESH_TOKEN_EXPIRE_DAYS=7

### API Configuration
API_HOST=0.0.0.0
API_PORT=8000
DEBUG=False
CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000,http://localhost:3001

### OpenAI API
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-key
OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4

### Google Cloud
GOOGLE_CLOUD_PROJECT=your-gcp-project-id
GOOGLE_API_KEY=your-google-api-key
GOOGLE_SPEECH_TO_TEXT_CREDENTIALS=path/to/credentials.json

### Email/SMTP
SMTP_SERVER=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=your-email@gmail.com
SMTP_PASSWORD=your-app-password
SMTP_FROM_EMAIL=noreply@bizflow.vn

### Celery
CELERY_BROKER=redis://localhost:6379
CELERY_BACKEND=redis://localhost:6379

### File Storage
STORAGE_TYPE=local
STORAGE_PATH=./uploads
MAX_UPLOAD_SIZE=10485760

## Web Frontend Configuration (.env.local)

### API
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8000/api

### Authentication
NEXT_PUBLIC_AUTH_ENABLED=true

### Features
NEXT_PUBLIC_ENABLE_AI_ORDERS=true
NEXT_PUBLIC_ENABLE_VOICE_INPUT=true

### Analytics
NEXT_PUBLIC_ANALYTICS_ENABLED=true
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=

### Timezone
NEXT_PUBLIC_TIMEZONE=Asia/Ho_Chi_Minh

## Mobile App Configuration (flutter/.env)

### API
API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000/api
API_TIMEOUT=30000

### Features
ENABLE_OFFLINE_MODE=true
ENABLE_BIOMETRIC=true
ENABLE_VOICE_INPUT=true

### Firebase
FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=bizflow-app
FIREBASE_API_KEY=

---

**NOTE**: Never commit real credentials to the repository. 
Use .env files locally and proper secret management in production.
